406
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:33,000
I was just

407
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:34,359
returning your favor.

408
00:24:35,400 --> 00:24:36,599
Didn't I tell you already?

409
00:24:36,599 --> 00:24:38,519
I really didn't write that letter.

410
00:24:38,519 --> 00:24:39,279
I understand.

