414
00:24:43,079 --> 00:24:43,639
I know.

415
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:44,720
Okay, let's not talk about it, then.

416
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:46,400
No.

417
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:48,079
Back then, I received
a lot of letters from my readers.

418
00:24:48,079 --> 00:24:48,799
I didn't know you back then.

419
00:24:48,799 --> 00:24:50,000
Why would I reply to your letter?

420
00:24:51,359 --> 00:24:52,159
You didn't write it?

421
00:24:53,039 --> 00:24:54,000
Who wrote it, then?

422
00:24:54,359 --> 00:24:55,159
Who knows?

423
00:24:55,319 --> 00:24:57,639
It might be one of your admirers.

424
00:24:59,279 --> 00:25:01,200
The boys who liked me then

425
00:25:02,079 --> 00:25:04,279
were Liao Xing, Zhu Baoming,

426
00:25:06,319 --> 00:25:07,519
and you.

427
00:25:12,039 --> 00:25:13,759
Did you write the letter?

428
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:16,640
No.

429
00:25:16,960 --> 00:25:18,359
That's impossible.

430
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:23,559
All right.

431
00:25:23,559 --> 00:25:24,839
Stop the PDA.

432
00:25:32,519 --> 00:25:34,079
What do you plan to do next?

433
00:25:35,079 --> 00:25:35,919
I haven't thought of it yet.

434
00:25:37,359 --> 00:25:38,439
I might start writing

435
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:39,720
my new story.

436
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:42,200
Can you reveal some sneak peeks,

437
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,480
the great author?

438
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:44,400
I haven't thought of it yet.

439
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:47,960
But are you willing
to be my first reader?

440
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:58,000
Of course!

441
00:26:01,920 --> 00:26:02,799
Pinky swear.

442
00:26:03,279 --> 00:26:04,039
Pinky swear.

443
00:26:04,319 --> 00:26:05,039
Cheers.

444
00:26:12,799 --> 00:26:13,720
So back then,

445
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:14,880
the letters from Ding Ye

446
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:15,839
were from you.

447
00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:16,759
That's right.

448
00:26:17,599 --> 00:26:19,159
Someone

449
00:26:19,759 --> 00:26:20,759
was so upset then.

450
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,359
She kept lingering around me.

451
00:26:22,359 --> 00:26:23,359
I found her bothersome.

452
00:26:24,759 --> 00:26:25,799
Why didn't you tell me, then?

453
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,240
The same one

454
00:26:28,480 --> 00:26:29,839
also told me firmly,

455
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:33,200
"I'll definitely meet Ding Ye one day.

456
00:26:33,519 --> 00:26:34,839
I empathize with his novels,

457
00:26:34,839 --> 00:26:36,440
so we'll surely be friends."

458
00:26:37,599 --> 00:26:39,159
You were so confident about it.

459
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:41,039
I couldn't bear to burst your bubble.

460
00:26:42,799 --> 00:26:44,000
You copied his handwriting,

461
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:45,200
and it looked exactly the same.

462
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:46,200
You put a lot
of effort into it, didn't you?

463
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,799
Well, it's nothing much.

464
00:26:49,079 --> 00:26:49,839
His handwriting

465
00:26:50,119 --> 00:26:51,039
is easy to copy.

466
00:26:52,960 --> 00:26:54,160
So,

467
00:26:54,720 --> 00:26:56,480
you, the weak student, were the one

468
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:58,359
who helped me
overcome the low point in my academics.

469
00:27:00,039 --> 00:27:01,839
So, what you've been keeping a secret

470
00:27:01,839 --> 00:27:03,480
is his bucket list?

471
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:04,599
That's right.

472
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,079
I made a promise,

473
00:27:06,079 --> 00:27:07,359
so I must not break it.

474
00:27:08,799 --> 00:27:09,960
I'm sorry

475
00:27:10,359 --> 00:27:11,559
for making you jealous.

476
00:27:12,079 --> 00:27:13,399
Who's jealous?

477
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:14,440
How is it possible?

478
00:27:15,119 --> 00:27:15,799
Do you still remember

479
00:27:15,799 --> 00:27:17,240
the nickname I gave you
when we were little?

480
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:18,759
Nickname?

481
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:22,319
Bull-Headed Jiang.

482
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:24,440
Okay, fine.

