486
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,279
Stop hugging me like that.

487
00:27:33,400 --> 00:27:34,000
Come here.

488
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:36,680
Is this okay?

489
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:43,119
You must have searched for me

