00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,279
Ninety-six.

520
00:28:59,519 --> 00:29:00,799
Ninety-five.

521
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:02,519
Ninety-four.

522
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:03,480
Huang Yingzi.

523
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:04,359
Where are you heading to?

524
00:29:04,359 --> 00:29:04,960
Ninety-two.

525
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:07,279
I'm going to a place
where no one else can find me.

526
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:08,880
Eighty-nine.

527
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:10,799
Eighty-eight.

528
00:29:19,680 --> 00:29:21,319
Three, two, one.

529
00:29:21,319 --> 00:29:22,599
Start.

530
00:29:35,720 --> 00:29:37,000
I got you.

531
00:29:38,720 --> 00:29:39,839
I got you!

532
00:29:39,839 --> 00:29:40,200
Come on.

533
00:29:43,079 --> 00:29:44,119
I got you!

534
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:44,640
Come on.

535
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:45,759
Let's find the rest.

536
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:53,039
Haven't you found Huang Yingzi yet?

537
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:54,880
- No.
- No.

538
00:29:54,880 --> 00:29:56,480
Has she gone home already?

539
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:56,839
That's right.

540
00:29:56,839 --> 00:29:58,599
She must have run back home

541
00:29:58,599 --> 00:30:00,039
in order to win us.

542
00:30:00,400 --> 00:30:01,839
She did that previously too.

543
00:30:02,759 --> 00:30:04,000
Let's go home, then.

544
00:30:05,079 --> 00:30:06,000
If I don't go home now,

545
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:07,839
my parents will get worried.

546
00:30:08,319 --> 00:30:09,480
Well, let's go, then.

547
00:30:09,480 --> 00:30:10,079
Come on.

548
00:30:12,960 --> 00:30:14,240
Let's see who will reach home first.

549
00:30:43,079 --> 00:30:44,519
Is anyone there?

550
00:30:45,599 --> 00:30:47,319
Save me.

551
00:30:48,599 --> 00:30:49,480
Yifei.

552
00:30:49,480 --> 00:30:50,440
Mingyu.

553
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:51,640
Are you there?

554
00:30:59,920 --> 00:31:01,119
Huang Yingzi.

555
00:31:02,119 --> 00:31:03,480
Please help me!

556
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:05,279
Huang Yingzi.

557
00:31:05,279 --> 00:31:07,400
Where are you, Huang Yingzi?

558
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,519
Huang Yingzi.

559
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:11,200
Huang Yingzi.

560
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,559
I'm here, Jiang Yi.

561
00:31:12,559 --> 00:31:13,680
Jiang Yi.

562
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:24,799
I'm here, Jiang Yi.

563
00:31:26,039 --> 00:31:27,079
Don't be scared.

564
00:31:27,079 --> 00:31:28,119
I'll stay by your side.

565
00:31:28,839 --> 00:31:30,919
The adults are coming to pick us up.

566
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:32,279
I thought

567
00:31:32,279 --> 00:31:34,599
you'd left me behind.

568
00:31:34,599 --> 00:31:35,399
I won't.

569
00:31:36,079 --> 00:31:37,319
No matter where you are,

570
00:31:37,319 --> 00:31:38,720
I'll find you.

571
00:31:41,799 --> 00:31:43,319
Stop crying.

572
00:31:59,279 --> 00:32:01,480
Jiang Yi. I didn't expect you

573
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:03,519
to have feelings for me since then!

574
00:32:03,519 --> 00:32:05,400
I didn't.

575
00:32:05,599 --> 00:32:07,359
You cried so pathetically

576
00:32:07,359 --> 00:32:08,199
and even got all snotty.

577
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:08,839
Who would like you?

578
00:32:09,279 --> 00:32:09,759
Then, tell me.

